residential.headline: LOCATION, QUALITY AND SUNNY ASPECT!!!
residential.description:
Defined by its contemporary and architecturally designed, bathed in the dappled light of a northeast aspect, this superb and stunning 3 bedrooms apartment is an idyllic family haven of character and charm. Located in the heart of Wentworthville within a stone's throw away to train station, shops, schools, library, major banks, medical centre and within easy access to M4, Cumberland Highway & Great Western Highway.
Features: • Three great size bedrooms fitted with built ins to all, large ensuite to main. • Modern open plan Kitchen fitted with stainless steel oven and gas cooktop, dishwasher and ducted range hood. • Bright spacious open planned lounge and dining area with timber flooring and reverse cycle air conditioning. • Beautiful main bathroom with separate bathtub and shower area • Home office/study area enclosed with extra storage. • Internal laundry and a secure car space with extra storage cage. •. North East paved courtyard ideal space to relax with morning coffee and breath in the fresh air.
It you want to live/invest close to all amenities, please do not miss the opportunity. Owner has made the decision to sell, so don't delay, your inspection is a must, please contact your exclusive agent Jitender Singh 0410 567 777 and Atul Bhanushali on 0402 961 515.
